obe_Bryant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, the Nike Kobe 4 \\\"Gold Medal\\\" is synonymous with greatness on the international stage.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Originally released in July 2009, the Nike Kobe 4 \\\"Gold Medal\\\" is back for the first time with modest tech upgrades and more hype than ever before.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Below is a detailed look and breakdown of the highly anticipated hoop shoes.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Nike Kobe 4 Protro \\\"Gold Medal\\\" drops on Monday, August 5.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.6696838038658881, \"rank\": 0.4779138684121777, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}, {\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\", \"score\": 0.9999661864167885, \"rank\": 3.381472649691441e-05, \"text\": \"Kobe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe_Bryant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Online shoppers can try to purchase the sneakers for $200 in adult sizes on the Nike SNKRS app and select retailers.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.6696838038658881, \"rank\": 0.4779138684121777, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Try is the key word as fans have had a challenging time purchasing Bryant's sneakers.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end